Catalogue of lists
------------------

(dd 26/6/98)

- Per player a file in xtrism/hisc/p<plrid>.thi
- Per team a file in xtrism/hisc/t<teamid>.thi
- All time heroes, a file containing both team and solo ATHs in
  xtrism/hisc/ath.thi

Each `pNN.thi' contains several lists: 
- the player's solo records for each brickset, plus one for each
  `special game profile'
- the player's team records idem (max one line per team) (equiv to an ath!)

Each `tNN.thi' contains several lists:
- the team's records for each brickset, plus one for each
  `special game profile'

`ath.thi' contains several lists:
- solo records for each brickset, plus one for each
  `special game profile'
- team records, idem, max one line per team.
